# ─── EmailJS Configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Create a FREE account at https://emailjs.com
# Then:
#   1. Create a Service (Gmail / Outlook) → copy the Service ID
#   2. Create an Email Template → copy the Template ID
#   3. Go to Account → API Keys → copy the Public Key
#
# Template variables used:
#   {{user_name}}   → sender's name
#   {{user_email}}  → sender's email (also set as Reply-To)
#   {{subject}}     → subject line (auto-generated from priority+name if left blank)
#   {{message}}     → message body
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
